# Vercel Environment Variables
# Add these in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables

# 1. WEB3_PROVIDER_URL
# Your Infura or Alchemy Sepolia testnet endpoint
# Get from: https://infura.io or https://alchemy.com
WEB3_PROVIDER_URL=https://sepolia.infura.io/v3/YOUR_PROJECT_ID

# 2. FACTORY_ADDRESS  
# Your deployed CampaignFactory contract address on Sepolia
# You'll get this after running: npm run deploy
FACTORY_ADDRESS=0xYourDeployedFactoryAddressHere

# NOTE: Do NOT add MNEMONIC_PHRASE to Vercel!
# Mnemonic is only needed locally for deployment, never in production
